com.pholser.junit.quickcheck.generator

Annotation Type Size


  • @Target(value={PARAMETER,FIELD,ANNOTATION_TYPE,TYPE_USE})
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @GeneratorConfiguration
public @interface Size

    Mark a parameter of a Property method with this annotation to constrain the size of values generated for the parameter.

    This annotation is recognized on array parameters and parameters of type Collection and Map.
